                "section_heading_layout": "section-heading--left",
                "custom_liquid": "<h1 class=\"unique-title-Yp8T4\">Our customers <span>love</span> the meals</h1>\n\n<div class=\"unique-container-Xr4D2a\">\n  <!-- Row 1 -->\n  <div class=\"unique-slider-wrapper-Rc9G7h\">\n    <div class=\"unique-slider-Rc9G7h\">\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/1.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_1_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Aysun, 32 🇹🇷</strong> Tam ev yemeği tadında, porsiyonlar da oldukça doyurucu.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0946/6350/8341/files/depositphotos_347242778-stock-photo-clean-groomed-look-handsome-caucasian.webp?v=1773908103\" alt=\"{{ review_2_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Sanne, 29 🇳🇱</strong> Alles was vers, warm en echt heel smaakvol.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/1.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_3_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Lukas, 34 🇩🇪</strong> Frisch, lecker und wie hausgemacht.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0946/6350/8341/files/depositphotos_12300646-stock-photo-portrait-of-relaxing-man-in.webp?v=1773908266\" alt=\"{{ review_4_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Lucas, 31 🇧🇪</strong> Heerlijk eten en topkwaliteit.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/3.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_5_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Ayşe, 30 🇹🇷</strong> Yoğun günlerde böyle kaliteli yemek bulmak büyük rahatlık.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Duplicate for seamless loop -->\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/1.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_1_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Emine, 32 🇹🇷</strong> Yemekler gerçekten çok lezzetliydi.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/2.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_2_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Sanne, 29 🇳🇱</strong> Eerlijk gezegd proef je echt dat dit met zorg is bereid.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/1.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_3_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Lukas, 34 🇩🇪</strong> Das Essen war frisch, lecker und überraschend authentisch.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/2.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_4_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Lucas, 31 🇧🇪</strong> Echt heerlijk gegeten. De gerechten zijn rijk van smaak en je merkt meteen de kwaliteit van de ingrediënten.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/3.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_5_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Ayşe, 30 🇹🇷</strong> Yoğun günlerde böyle kaliteli yemek bulmak büyük rahatlık.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Row 2 (Reverse direction) -->\n  <div class=\"unique-slider-wrapper-Rc9G7h unique-reverse\">\n    <div class=\"unique-slider-Rc9G7h\">\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/3.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_6_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Emma, 27 🇳🇱</strong> Royale porties en heerlijk van smaak.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/4.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_7_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Zeynep, 35 🇹🇷</strong> Gerçekten çok başarılı bir lezzet.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/4.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_8_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Jonas, 33 🇧🇪</strong> Super tevreden. Smaakvol en vullend.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/5.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_9_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Leonie, 28 🇩🇪</strong> Mit Abstand die besten. Frisch und hochwertig.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/5.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_10_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Suat, 29 🇹🇷</strong> Düzenli sipariş vereceğim bir yer oldu.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Duplicate for seamless loop -->\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/3.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_6_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Emma, 27 🇳🇱</strong> Royale porties en echt huisgemaakte smaak.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/4.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_7_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Zeynep, 35 🇹🇷</strong> İlk siparişimde bu kadar memnun kalacağımı düşünmemiştim.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/4.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_8_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Jonas, 33 🇧🇪</strong> Super tevreden. De maaltijden zijn smaakvol, vullend en ideaal voor drukke werkdagen.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/5.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_9_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Leonie, 28 🇩🇪</strong> Mit Abstand die besten Liefergerichte.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"unique-card-Lj6Z8k\">\n        <img class=\"unique-image-Ys3Kv9\" src=\"https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/5.jpg\" alt=\"{{ review_10_alt | default: 'User Image' }}\">\n        <p><strong>Ahmet, 29 🇹🇷</strong> Sanki mutfakta biri benim için özel hazırlamış gibi hissettirdi.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script:wght@700&display=swap');\n\n  .unique-title-Yp8T4 {\n    font-size: {{ title_font_size | default: '18px' }};\n    font-weight: {{ title_font_weight | default: 'bold' }};\n    color: #0d0d0d;\n    margin-bottom: {{ title_margin_bottom | default: '15px' }};\n    text-align: {{ title_alignment | default: 'center' }};\n  }\n\n  .unique-title-Yp8T4 span {\n    font-family: {{ highlight_font_family | default: 'Dancing Script, cursive' }};\n    font-size: {{ highlight_font_size | default: '36px' }};\n    background: #47296B;\n    -webkit-background-clip: text;\n    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n    font-weight: {{ highlight_font_weight | default: 'bold' }};\n  }\n\n  .unique-container-Xr4D2a {\n    width: 100%;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    position: relative;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: {{ rows_gap | default: '20px' }};\n    padding: {{ container_padding | default: '0' }};\n  }\n\n  .unique-slider-wrapper-Rc9G7h {\n    display: flex;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    position: relative;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n\n  .unique-slider-Rc9G7h {